gateway.svg — original work, part of this project.

pi.svg — original work, part of this project. A stylised single-board computer
(Raspberry Pi), not derived from any trademarked logo.

cloud.svg — original work, part of this project. A generic cloud glyph (the
cloud-subgraph hub), not derived from any provider's trademark.

cloud-storage.svg — original work, part of this project. A generic stacked
data-store glyph, not derived from any provider's trademark.

claude.svg — the Claude mark, used to identify the LLM-agent cloud node.

substack.svg — original work, part of this project. A generic feed/blog glyph in
the style of the open RSS feed mark, for the content-sink connector. Deliberately
NOT any provider's logo. (The DreameHome cloud node reuses dreame.png.)

google.svg — original work, part of this project. A generic scan/vision glyph
(targeting ring, iris, pupil), not derived from any provider's trademark or logo.

roomba-wheel.svg — original work, part of this project. A stylised rally-car
alloy wheel (the two Roomba Rally nodes), not derived from any trademarked mark.

